4. Mike’s proof that [Σ S¹ Cover] is contractible
5. Proof with the flattening lemma that [Σ S¹ S¹Cover] is contractible
6. Proof of [Ω S¹ ≃ ℤ] using the fact that [Σ S¹ S¹Cover] is contractible (common
